    Description:
    The Elim Community Food Pantry provides free food to feed families and individuals in need. We supply groceries for residents that do not have enough food because they lack the resources to purchase it. We serve everyone that comes to the pantry, regardless of their race, color, or religion.

    This program provides:

    - Foods to meet basic nutritional needs
